FROM golang:1.13

ENV BUILD_DIR /app

RUN mkdir -p $BUILD_DIR
WORKDIR $BUILD_DIR


RUN apt-get update && \
apt-get install --no-install-recommends ruby-dev -y
RUN gem install fpm --no-ri --no-rdoc

COPY . $BUILD_DIR/
